item.title: Day # whatever of me trying to change people’s minds about spiders
item.description: Alright everyone, time for a little more hardcore spider action! This is Mare, my 2 year old Grammostola rosea, or Chilean rose hair tarantula. I’ve had her since she was the size of the nail on my pinky finger. She’s still got a lot of growing to do, and it’s been surprisingly fun raising her up! She’s got a totally different personality than my other T, Lucienne, even though they’re closely related As you can see, even though she’s big and maybe a little intimidating, she’s also calm and sweet. She doesn’t mind being handled; she usually kicks a few hairs but has never threat posed let alone bitten anyone :) #spider #nature #cute #tarantula #photography
